igilant against phishing on public Wi-Fi; avoid suspicious links and never\nenter sensitive information on unsecured networks\n\nTip 10: Use a Secure DNS Server\n\nUse a secure DNS server to protect against DNS spoofing and ensure a safer\nbrowsing experience on public Wi-Fi.\n\nLearn more\n\nAd\n\n", "frontpage": false}
